348void ShowShareSheet::callReply(IPC::Decoder& decoder, CompletionHandler<void(bool&&)>&& completionHandler)
349{
350 std::optional<bool> granted;
351 decoder >> granted;
352 if (!granted) {
353 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
354 cancelReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
355 return;
356 }
357 completionHandler(WTFMove(*granted));
358}
359
360void ShowShareSheet::cancelReply(CompletionHandler<void(bool&&)>&& completionHandler)
361{
362 completionHandler(IPC::AsyncReplyError<bool>::create());
363}
364
365void ShowShareSheet::send(UniqueRef<IPC::Encoder>&& encoder, IPC::Connection& connection, bool granted)
366{
367 encoder.get() << granted;
368 connection.sendSyncReply(WTFMove(encoder));
369}

516#if ENABLE(MEDIA_STREAM)
517
518void EnumerateMediaDevicesForFrame::callReply(IPC::Decoder& decoder, CompletionHandler<void(Vector<WebCore::CaptureDevice>&&, String&&)>&& completionHandler)
519{
520 std::optional<Vector<WebCore::CaptureDevice>> devices;
521 decoder >> devices;
522 if (!devices) {
523 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
524 cancelReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
525 return;
526 }
527 std::optional<String> mediaDeviceIdentifierHashSalt;
528 decoder >> mediaDeviceIdentifierHashSalt;
529 if (!mediaDeviceIdentifierHashSalt) {
530 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
531 cancelReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
532 return;
533 }
534 completionHandler(WTFMove(*devices), WTFMove(*mediaDeviceIdentifierHashSalt));
535}
536
537void EnumerateMediaDevicesForFrame::cancelReply(CompletionHandler<void(Vector<WebCore::CaptureDevice>&&, String&&)>&& completionHandler)
538{
539 completionHandler(IPC::AsyncReplyError<Vector<WebCore::CaptureDevice>>::create(), IPC::AsyncReplyError<String>::create());
540}
541
542void EnumerateMediaDevicesForFrame::send(UniqueRef<IPC::Encoder>&& encoder, IPC::Connection& connection, const Vector<WebCore::CaptureDevice>& devices, const String& mediaDeviceIdentifierHashSalt)
543{
544 encoder.get() << devices;
545 encoder.get() << mediaDeviceIdentifierHashSalt;
546 connection.sendSyncReply(WTFMove(encoder));
547}
548
549#endif
